---
title: Login Flow (Desktop Application)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant LV as LoginView
    participant AUTH as AuthenticationService
    participant JDBC as JdbcTemplate
    participant DB as SQLite

    U->>LV: Enter email + password
    LV->>AUTH: authenticateUser(email, password)
    AUTH->>JDBC: SELECT user by normalized email
    JDBC->>DB: Execute query
    DB-->>JDBC: User row with password_hash
    JDBC-->>AUTH: Result set
    AUTH->>AUTH: Hash provided password and compare

    alt Credentials valid
        AUTH-->>LV: User object
        LV->>LV: Build DashboardView
        LV-->>U: Switch scene to dashboard
    else Credentials invalid
        AUTH-->>LV: null
        LV-->>U: Display "Invalid email or password."
    end
